<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Special Text Formatting</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Special Text Formatting</h1>

  <h2>Emphasized Text</h2>
  <p>This is an <em>emphasized</em> text.</p>

  <h2>Marked Text</h2>
  <p>This is <mark>marked</mark> text.</p>

  <h2>Inserted Text</h2>
  <p>This is <ins>inserted</ins> text.</p>

  <h2>Subscript and Superscript Text</h2>
  <p>H<sub>2</sub>O is the formula for water.</p>
  <p>2<sup>3</sup> is equal to 8.</p>

  <h2>Deleted Text</h2>
  <p>This text <del>should be deleted</del>.</p>

  <h2>Bold and Italic Text</h2>
  <p>This is <b>bold</b> text.</p>
  <p>This is <i>italic</i> text.</p>
  <p>This is <b><i>bold and italic</i></b> text.</p>
</body>
</html>
